<div class="row"><div class="rowInner">            <div class="panels" columns="3">                 <div class="col">    <div class="editable">        <div class="itemHead">    <a href="https://ije-blog.com/">        <img src="https://static.primary.prod.gcms.the-infra.com/static/site/ije/image/ije-blog.jpg?node=8be9865e47d30051879b&amp;version=87543:b9c1eaffcf2987729914" alt="IJE blog">    </a></div><div class="itemBody">    <h3>        <a href="https://ije-blog.com/">            <p>IJEblog</p>        </a>    </h3>    <p>The IJEblog contextualises and provides insight into epidemiological research related to the Journal’s publication programme. It aims to make the latest epidemiological discoveries accessible to an audience beyond the Journal’s traditional readership, encourage debate, and help authors maximise the impact of their research.</p><p><a data-link-id="ff2b7bbe-ed90-458e-aa8b-0339da50d2e1" href="https://ije-blog.com/">Explore the full collection of blog articles here</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p></div>    </div></div>                             <div class="col">    <div class="editable">        <div class="itemHead">    <a href="https://academic.oup.com/ije/pages/app">        <img src="https://static.primary.prod.gcms.the-infra.com/static/site/ije/image/ije-app.jpg?node=909aa1e2c072166339b5&amp;version=87546:5a1f138fc30a7ba60be1" alt="IJE app">    </a></div><div class="itemBody">    <h3>        <a href="https://academic.oup.com/ije/pages/app">            <p>IJE app</p>        </a>    </h3>    <p>The International Journal of Epidemiology (IJE) app allows you to read IJE content on the move using your smartphone or tablet device.</p><p><a data-link-id="b8e61625-75e6-416f-91c4-cb44e776991b" href="https://academic.oup.com/ije/pages/app">Read more about the app</a></p></div>    </div></div>                             <div class="col">    <div class="editable">        <div class="itemHead">    <a href="http://ieaweb.org/">        <img src="https://static.primary.prod.gcms.the-infra.com/static/site/ije/image/IEA.png?node=97b8abc78ba8dff2f852&amp;version=87548:8a6fd8a723a653534428" alt="IEA">    </a></div><div class="itemBody">    <h3>        <a href="http://ieaweb.org/">            <p>About IEA</p>        </a>    </h3>    <p>The IEA aim to facilitate communication amongst those engaged in research and teaching of epidemiology throughout the world, and to encourage its use in all fields of health including social, community, and preventative medicine.</p><p><a data-link-id="47cef1b4-a68b-4e84-bc07-c6c2e2db9a9c" href="http://ieaweb.org/">Visit the society website</a></p></div>    </div></div>             </div></div></div><div class="row"><div class="rowInner">            <div class="panels" columns="3">                 <div class="col">    <div class="editable">        <div class="itemHead">    <a href="https://academic.oup.com/journals/pages/authors/promoting_your_article/article_level_metrics">        <img src="https://static.primary.prod.gcms.the-infra.com/static/site/journals/image/shared/altmetric.jpg?node=5d7d63451fe52d2bb31a&amp;version=93940:72e5df6fa0e098252700" alt="Altmetric logo">    </a></div><div class="itemBody">    <h3>        <a href="https://academic.oup.com/journals/pages/authors/promoting_your_article/article_level_metrics">            <p>Altmetrics</p>        </a>    </h3>    <p>Discover a more complete picture of how readers engage with research in <em>International Journal of Epidemiology&nbsp;</em>through Altmetric data. Now available on article pages.</p></div>    </div></div>                             <div class="col">    <div class="editable">        <div class="itemHead">    <a href="https://academic.oup.com/journals/pages/librarians/library_recommendation_form">        <img src="https://static.primary.prod.gcms.the-infra.com/static/site/journals/image/shared/library-recommend.jpg?node=a5634845081f206d0b24&amp;version=98697:aadcac7b2a928ef31879" alt="Recommend to your library">    </a></div><div class="itemBody">    <h3>        <a href="https://academic.oup.com/journals/pages/librarians/library_recommendation_form">            <p>Recommend to your library</p>        </a>    </h3>    <p autocomplete="off" name="text">Fill out our simple online form to recommend <em>International Journal of Epidemiology</em> to your library.</p><p autocomplete="off" name="text"><a data-link-id="270d6dcd-6272-48a4-8db2-0d1cab9254d0" href="https://academic.oup.com/journals/pages/librarians/library_recommendation_form">Recommend now</a></p></div>    </div></div>                             <div class="col">    <div class="editable">        <div class="itemHead">    <a href="https://academic.oup.com/journals/pages/authors">        <img src="https://static.primary.prod.gcms.the-infra.com/static/site/journals/image/shared/author-resource-center.jpg?node=d5478c25b375501bb037&amp;version=93940:72e5df6fa0e098252700" alt="Author resources">    </a></div><div class="itemBody">    <h3>        <a href="https://academic.oup.com/journals/pages/authors">            <p>Author resources</p>        </a>    </h3>    <p autocomplete="off" name="text">Learn about how to submit your article, our publishing process, and tips on how to promote your article.</p><p autocomplete="off" name="text"><a data-link-id="657678ff-2f2f-4329-85d8-06648acf3017" href="https://academic.oup.com/journals/pages/authors">Find out more</a></p></div>    </div></div>             </div></div></div><div class="row relatedJournals">    <div class="rowInner">                <div class="rowHead">            <h3>Related Titles<span class="underbar journal-bg"></span></h3>        </div>                <div class="relatedJournalsBody">                            <a href="https://academic.oup.com/ajh"><img alt="Cover image of current issue from American Journal of Hypertension" src="https://academic.oup.com/ajh/current/cover/small"><span class="relatedTitleText">American Journal of Hypertension</span></a>                            <a 